From 7195320734cc907f00fefdb4a190451adce040b5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: VTK Compatibility <vtk@vtk.org>
Date: Thu, 30 Apr 2026 23:49:18 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] macOS: Add gcc-14 and 10.5/10.6 SDK compatibility

This patch adds support for building VTK with gcc-14 and targeting
Mac OS X 10.5/10.6 systems with their respective SDKs.

Changes include:

vtkCocoaMacOSXSDKCompatibility.h:
- Lower minimum SDK requirement from 10.7 to 10.5
- Add __has_feature() fallback for gcc (clang-specific)
- Add portable VTK_DIAG_OFF/VTK_DIAG_ON macros for diagnostic suppression
- Add NSOpenGLPFAOpenGLProfile and related constants for <10.7 SDKs
- Add helper functions with runtime checks for 10.7+ backing APIs:
  - vtkCocoaConvertPointToBacking/vtkCocoaConvertRectToBacking
  - vtkCocoaConvertSizeFromBacking/vtkCocoaConvertPointFromBacking
  - vtkCocoaSetWantsBestResolutionOpenGLSurface
  - vtkCocoaGetBackingScaleFactor

vtkCocoaGLView.h:
- Make NSDraggingDestination protocol conformance conditional (10.7+)

vtkCocoaGLView.mm:
- Replace @[] array literals with [NSArray arrayWithObject:] for gcc
- Replace fast enumeration (for-in) with NSEnumerator for gcc
- Replace #pragma clang diagnostic with VTK_DIAG_OFF/ON macros
- Use backing API helper functions instead of direct method calls

vtkCocoaRenderWindowInteractor.mm:
- Replace fast enumeration with NSEnumerator for gcc

vtkCocoaRenderWindow.mm:
- Replace #pragma clang diagnostic with VTK_DIAG_OFF/ON macros
- Replace setWantsBestResolutionOpenGLSurface with helper function
- Use backing API helper functions with respondsToSelector checks
  for convertRectToBacking/convertRectFromBacking on NSWindow/NSScreen
